p/B_BL-dKp5dG/|title=\u201cBLAME IT ON BABY\u201d \ud83d\udcbf 4-17-20\u2757\ufe0f (@dababy) \u2022 Instagram photos and videos|date=|via=Instagram|access-date=April 15, 2020}}</ref> \n\nThe album is supported by the single \"[[Find My Way]]\", released on April 1, 2020.\n\n== Background ==\nThe project is DaBaby's third studio album. He first announced the album on April 13, 2020, with a post on [[Twitter]], and revealed the cover art and release date on April 14.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/DaBabyDaBaby/status/1249735312907079680|title=DaBaby on Twitter: \"THIS FRIDAY! \ud83e\udd2b\ud83d\udcbf\" / Twitter|via=Twitter|access-date=April 15, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B-9tfDGJF1m/|title=\u201cBLAME IT ON BABY\u201d \ud83d\udcbf 4-17-20\u2757\ufe0f (@dababy) \u2022 Instagram photos and videos|last=|first=|date=|via=Instagram|access-date=April 15, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hypebeast.com/2020/4/dababy-announces-new-album-blame-it-on-baby-release-date|title=DaBaby Announces New Album 'Blame It On Baby'|last=|first=|date=|website=[[Hypebeast]]|access-date=April 15, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vulture.com/2020/04/dababy-new-album-blame-it-on-baby-release-date.html|title=DaBaby Dons a Face Mask and Safely Announces New Album|last=|first=|date=|website=[[Vulture (website)|Vulture]]|access-date=April 15, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hiphopdx.com/news/id.55432/title.dababy-announces-blame-it-on-baby-album|title=DaBaby Announces 'Blame It On Baby' Album|last=|first=|date=|website=[[HipHopDX]]|access-date=April 15, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/9357077/dababy-teasing-new-music|title=Is DaBaby Dropping New Music on Friday?|last=|first=|date=|website=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|access-date=April 15, 2020}}</ref>\n\n== Promotion ==\n\n=== Singles ===\n* \"[[Find My Way]]\" was released as the album's lead single on April 1, 2020, along with a music video.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.complex.com/music/2020/04/dababy-find-my-way-video|title=Watch DaBaby's Short Film for New Song \"Find My Way\"|last=|first=|date=|website=[[Complex (magazine)|Complex]]|access-date=April 15, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Track listing==\nCredits adapted from [[Tidal (service)|Tidal]].<ref name=\"Tidal\">{{cite web|url=https://listen.tidal.com/album/137748764|title=BLAME IT ON BABY / DaBaby|website=[[Tidal (service)|Tidal]]|accessdate=April 17, 2020}}</ref>\n\n{{Track listing\n| extra_column = Producer(s)\n| total_length = 33:34\n\n| title1 = Can't Stop\n| writer1 = {{hlist|[[DaBaby|Jonathan Kirk]]|Michael Hernandez|John Lucas|Carlos Godwin}}\n| extra1 = {{hlist|Foreign Teck|JW Lucas|Lostheproducer}}\n| length1 = 2:48\n\n| title2 = Pick Up\n| note2 = featuring [[Quavo]]\n| writer2 = {{hlist|Kirk|[[Quavious Marshall|Quavo]]|Dejuane Dunwood}}\n| extra2 = DJ Kid\n| length2 = 1:58\n\n| title3 = Lightskin Shit\n| note3 = featuring [[Future (rapper)|Future]]\n| writer3 = {{hlist|Kirk|[[Future (rapper)|Nayvadius Wilburn]]|Tahj Morgan|Tobias Dekker}}\n| extra3 = {{hlist|JetsonMade|Outtatown|Starboy}}\n| length3 = 1:51\n\n| title4 = Talk About It\n| writer4 = {{hlist|Kirk|Nils Noehden|[[Wheezy (record producer)|Wesley Glass]]}}\n| extra4 = {{hlist|Nils|[[Wheezy (record producer)|Wheezy]]}}\n| length4 = 2:39\n\n| title5 = Sad Shit\n| writer5 = {{hlist|Kirk|Dunwood|Thomas French}}\n| extra5 = {{hlist|DJ Kid|Tom French}}\n| length5 = 3:37\n\n| title6 = [[Find My Way (DaBaby song)|Find My Way]]\n| writer6 = {{hlist|Kirk|Dunwood}}\n| extra6 = DJ Kid\n| length6 = 2:19\n\n| title7 = Rockstar\n| note7 = featuring [[Roddy Ricch]]\n| writer7 = {{hlist|Kirk|[[Roddy Ricch|Rodrick Moore Jr.]]|Ross Portaro IV}}\n| extra7 = SethInTheKitchen\n| length7 = 3:01\n\n| title8 = Jump\n| note8 = featuring [[YoungBoy Never Broke Again]]\n| writer8 = {{hlist|Kirk|[[YoungBoy Never Broke Again|Kentrell Gaulden]]|[[A Boogie wit da Hoodie|Artist Dubose]]|Dunwood}}\n| 